    <note>Zhao(1) Xuzhi [20559] He was director of the Tanzhou Southern Sacred Mountain Temple, probably a nominal office, since he died in Jiujiang during the flight South. His wife #2, born Zhang(1), took her stepson, Gongheng [20560] (q.v.), to Jinxian where she relied on her various fathers (zhufu, i.e. uncles) in order to support the family. I date the move to Jinxian county with Xuzhi even though he did not live to reach his new home. SS(PRC), 238.8287.</note>
